latestIgtvVideos.title: **Chicken Momo Recipe**
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Okay so before telling you the recipe I want to tell you that the taste of momo is really good, I would say it will b beyond ur expectations. After learning it I nvr went to the momo shop. 
The momo recipe is this much good. 
This is the authentic style momo recipe which I have learnt from my senior sis @hlimeefebberry
Thank you hlimi di for teaching me.
.
. 
Try it and let me know whether you like it or not. And if you have any queries regarding this momo recipe then let me know in the comment section, will surely ans you. 
. 
. 
Chicken Momo recipe :
Ingredients for chicken cheema :
Chicken(500g)
Onion (350g)
Refined oil(150ml)
Ginger paste(1tbsp)
Salt(3-4tbsp)
.
. 
Ingredients for chutney :
Onion(2medium size) 
Garlic (7-8clove)
Ginger paste 1tsp
Tomato (2pcs)
Dry chilli (10pcs)
Mustard oil (3tbsp)
Turmeric (1/2tsp)
Salt (2tbsp)
#For chutney at first boiled the tomato and dry chilli. And add a little amount of water while grinding it.
.
. 
*For procedure watch the full video.
.
. 
**Note: Don't add garlic or chilli in the cheema mixture. Don't add oil or salt in maida while making the dough.
